snippet.title: Blue Prince Release Window Trailer
snippet.description:
Blue Prince, the atmospheric architectural adventure is coming to Steam and Windows in Spring 2025! Soon you will be able to explore the ever-changing manor of 45 rooms in your search for the mysterious and elusive Room 46. Will you strategic mind, puzzle-solving skills and explorations help you find it? 

Wishlist today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1569580/Blue_Prince/
